1440
01:17:22,463 --> 01:17:23,794
- Mrs. Steuby.
- Bye, dear.

1441
01:17:23,964 --> 01:17:27,593
- Mrs. Steuby, I don't want pedal pushers.
- No, no. You'll look great.

