01:17:30,471 --> 01:17:32,268
It's okay.

1443
01:17:32,439 --> 01:17:35,602
It's okay. No big deal.
Just pretend like I don't have it.

1444
01:17:36,210 --> 01:17:38,337
I hear you're planning to bid on Bryce.

1445
01:17:38,512 --> 01:17:40,275
